data.description: Welcome to the cottages at Diablo Grande. This 3 bedroom 2.5 bathroom home is move in ready! Features approximately 1,806 Sq Ft, open kitchen to living room, fireplace with starter and ceiling fans throughout. All bedrooms are upstairs as well as the laundry room. Primary bedroom opens to a veranda overlooking the neighborhood. Large drive-in garage with additional uncovered parking in the front. Close vicinity to park. This development is secluded and protected with 24 hour manned security at the front entry gate.
